What did ancient Chinese call people from other nations?;Barbarians
Built in ancient times, what links two great rivers of China today?;The Grand Canal
Name two medieval Chinese dynasties?;Sui, Tang, or Song
What trade route linked Asia to the rest of the world?;The Silk Road
Under the Tang, how did a person get a government job?;He took a test.
What was invented under the Song Dynasty?;Gunpowder, paper, block printing, advanced navigational tools.
